{
  "stem": "22660.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had heard about Michael Reese through my aunt and uncle who's-- my aunt's brother was Professor Oppenheimer, was at Michael Reese Hospital.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's how-- that's what I wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the only problem was when I came to the United States, my college degree from Montevideo was not recognized.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't-- that was not what they could use here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I had to go back to night school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In order to become a medical technologist, you had to have two years of college, so alongside my training at Michael Reese, I went to night school to the University of Chicago.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Actually, I had finished my 18 months course as a medical technologist prior to really finishing college.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had six more months to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so that's how that happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the south side of Chicago.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I lived at 67th and Kimbark.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A German-Jewish family was renting rooms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I rented a room there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but then that room-- their son came back from the Army and I had to move out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I moved downstairs to a lovely Jewish family whose three daughters had just gotten married.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were lonely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so for $8 a week, I-- [LAUGHS] I had breakfast and I had dinner.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was really very, very lucky, very lucky.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At Michael Reese Hospital.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My very first job before I went to Michael Reese, I sold hats in a little shop at the Palmer House.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That was my very first job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I wanted to-- I wanted to really get to Michael Reese.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and I accomplished it that I could take my training there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, actually, you asked my very first job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now you ask me, did I know English?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew very, very little.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
